Interface EquivalentURI

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EquivalentURIImpl

    public interface EquivalentURI
    For a URI this object holds its equivalent URI, the proximity of the equivalent to the original URI and the schema URI that the equivalent URI belongs to.
